OL,5, Oscar-winning actor Dame Helen Mirren  
OL,6, has told the BBC there is a "very      
OL,7, delicate balance" to playing people    
OL,8, with a different heritage.             
OL,10,FMirren, 78, portrays former Israeli    
OL,11,FPrime Minister Golda Meir in her latest
OL,12,Ffilm - a role which has attracted some 
OL,13,Fcriticism because she is not Jewish.   
OL,15,FShe told Laura Kuenssberg on her Sunday
OL,16,Fprogramme she "can see" why some may be
OL,17,Funcomfortable with the portrayal.      
OL,19,F"But sometimes I can't see because I   
OL,20,Fcan't see who in this room is Jewish." 
